HEADWORD: Uriniparous
<hw>U`ri*nip"a*rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Urine</ets> + L. <ets>parere</ets> to produce: cf. F.
<ets>urinipare</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Producing or
